title: Page Name
description: The human-readable title or name of the web page or app screen viewed by the user. Commonly corresponds to the <title> tag of the page or the logical name of the screen in mobile applications. Used to identify and categorize user navigation and engagement patterns across the site or app.

tags.label: Cross-Industry (applicable to all digital analytics implementations)
